</li></ul> 
OSG resources were regularly used in data analysis leading to CDF publications starting in 2006.  <ul>
<li> Damjanovi, A., et al. Open Science Grid study of the coupling between conformation and water content in the interior of a protein. Journal of Physical Chemistry, B, August 2008. 
